description: Returns a list of job templates. Requires permission to access the ListJobTemplates action.

nested_items.name: jobTemplates
nested_items.description: A list of objects that contain information about the job templates.

nested_items.name: jobTemplateArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the job template.

nested_items.name: jobTemplateId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the job template.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: A description of the job template.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time, in seconds since the epoch, when the job template was created.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no additional results.
